tweet: I am facing two right-wing opponents.   And neither will say whether they would continue the CA DOJ’s efforts to strengthen life-saving gun laws, uphold Roe v. Wade, and defend our trans youth.  This November, let’s defend our rights & protect our communities. #CADem2022
